flowchart LR
  Start["首次进入 App"] --> Path{"选择规划路径"}
  Path --> Vision["深度愿景<br/>五年愿景 -> 年度 OKR -> 季度 OKR -> 4 周承诺"]
  Path --> Quick["快速规划<br/>季度目标 -> 本周重点 + 今日建议"]
  Path --> Manual["手动 OKR<br/>年 -> 季 -> 月 -> 周 -> 今日，可留空"]

  Vision --> Confirm["用户确认 / 修改 AI 草案"]
  Quick --> Confirm
  Manual --> Confirm
  Confirm --> Focus["本周重点<br/>3-5 条方向锚点"]
  Focus --> Todo["今日清单<br/>手动 CRUD / AI 建议"]
  Todo --> Energy["每日能量记录<br/>0-100 主观推进"]
  Energy --> WeekAverage["本周累计<br/>按已记录天数均值"]
  WeekAverage --> Settlement["周结算<br/>建议分 + 用户最终确认"]
  Settlement --> Fruit["每周果实<br/>时间胶囊快照"]
  Fruit --> Tree["年度成长树<br/>季度阶段 + 荣誉层"]
  Tree --> Review["回看成长<br/>低频正反馈"]
  Review -.-> Focus

  Todo -.->|"任务完成只作参考<br/>不自动决定能量分"| Energy
  Settlement -.->|"结算快照防止历史漂移"| Fruit
  Tree -.->|"季度均值达标时新增永久荣誉"| Honor["QuarterHonor<br/>只增不减"]

  classDef product fill:#064e3b,stroke:#86efac,color:#f0fdf4
  classDef decision fill:#713f12,stroke:#fde68a,color:#fffbeb
  classDef reward fill:#4c1d95,stroke:#ddd6fe,color:#faf5ff

  class Start,Vision,Quick,Manual,Confirm,Focus,Todo,Energy,WeekAverage,Settlement product
  class Path decision
  class Fruit,Tree,Review,Honor reward
